# Pine Script v6 — Cursor Rules
# Maintainer: Ugur Pala · mail@ugurpala.com

## TR | Türkçe — Kod Kuralları
- Her script `//@version=6` ile başlar
- `ta.*` fonksiyonlarını kullan, manuel yeniden yazmaya gerek yok
- `var` / `varip` kullanımını execution model'e göre yap
- Kod yazmadan önce mutlaka `LESSONS_LEARNED.md` oku
- `LLM_MANIFEST.md` ile doğru referans dosyasını bul

## EN | English — Code Rules
- Every script starts with `//@version=6`
- Use `ta.*` functions — never reimplement them
- Use `var` / `varip` correctly per the execution model
- Always read `LESSONS_LEARNED.md` before writing code
- Use `LLM_MANIFEST.md` to find the correct reference file

## Reference Map / Referans Haritası

| Need / İhtiyaç | File / Dosya |
|----------------|-------------|
| RSI, EMA, MACD, crossover, ATR | `reference/functions/ta.md` |
| strategy.entry, exit, position | `reference/functions/strategy.md` |
| plot, line, box, label, table | `reference/functions/drawing.md` |
| request.security, MTF | `reference/functions/request.md` |
| array, map, matrix | `reference/functions/collections.md` |
| math, str, input, alert | `reference/functions/general.md` |
| var, varip, barstate | `concepts/execution_model.md` |
| Errors / Hatalar | `concepts/common_errors.md` |
| **Always first / Her zaman önce** | `LESSONS_LEARNED.md` |

## On Error / Hata Olduğunda
TR: Hatayı çözünce hemen `LESSONS_LEARNED.md` dosyasına ekle.
EN: After solving an error, immediately append it to `LESSONS_LEARNED.md`.
